                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 177 was first discussed by the National
                    Security Council at the meeting held January 8, 1954. The conversation on that
                    occasion was devoted entirely to Indochinese questions. For the pertinent
                    section of the memorandum of discussion, see <ref
                        target="frus1952-54v13p1#pg_947">volume XIII, Part 1, page 947</ref>.</p>
            </div>
